[pr'thak] The
fact the body and the Self are distinct [bahudhA gItam] has been told in many ways- [r'Shibhi:] by many Rishis, [vividhai: ChandObhi:] by various Vedas, [brahmasUtra padai:] by the verses of the Brahmasutra.

